{"type": "article", "id": 3905, "title": "Utsusiwa 系列陶瓷餐具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-27T07:57:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233117CQfUpbOJEyS8q6sm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本 Ryosuke Fukusada 设计工作室推出的一套餐具系列 Utsusiwa 目前正在东京 IFFT 举行的Interior Life Style Living 2014 展览上展出。Utsusiwa 系列全部由陶瓷制作而成，设计团队将我们常见的饼干、塑料包装泡沫、泡泡包装隔离层等常见的纹理运用在了餐具的表面，给人视觉吸引力的同时，亦创造了独特的触感。整个制作工艺皆由京都当地的传统手工作坊完成。目前，Ryosuke Fukusada 的线上店铺正在筹备，想要购买的朋友们还得等等。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233114QsL3hyCE6UATr70I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233114jglH75VaDBteK4pd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233115vjy8EYZwqobutkCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233116Ws9wCqn32ycNjTLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233116WM2vXUPw9tO3R6yF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}